      <title>WSP Global 陷入卖空者瞄准，股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/wsp-global-caught-in-short-seller-s-crosshairs-shares-tumble</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Spruce Point Capital Management LLC 表示正在做空这家加拿大工程公司的股票，并给予其“强力卖出”建议后，WSP Global Inc. 股价暴跌。]]></description>
